### What This Repo Is
- A standalone **cognitive kernel runtime** (‚ÄúOS mode‚Äù) that schedules agentic sub-processes, routes IPC (signals + blackboard), and runs metacognition/awareness layers.
- A first-party **observability stack (‚ÄúLens‚Äù)** that turns protocol events + snapshots into WebSocket-delivered, UI-friendly deltas.
- A **run manager** that starts kernel runs (child-process model) and supports DB-backed storage (Neon/Postgres) for cross-machine observability.
- Optional **control planes**: HTTP API (Hono) and MCP server (Model Context Protocol).

